    </tr>
</table>

<p>Mix all the ingredients together and pack in a lunch container. This pasta salad can be made ahead of time and stored in the fridge for up to two days.</p>

<h3>3. Gluten-Free Snack Boxes</h3>

<p>Snack boxes are perfect for picky eaters because they offer a variety of small, bite-sized options. Here’s an example of a gluten-free snack box:</p>

