        <td>1/2 cup</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Hard-boiled egg</td>
        <td>1</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p>This snack box is not only gluten-free but also provides a good balance of protein, healthy fats, and carbohydrates.</p>

<h3>4. Gluten-Free Muffins and Baked Goods</h3>

<p>Baking your own gluten-free muffins or cookies can be a great way to ensure that your child has a tasty and safe treat in their lunchbox. Here’s a simple recipe for gluten-free banana muffins:</p>

